# Omarchy Package List (AUR, GitHub, and Local)
# Supports AUR packages, GitHub repositories, and local PKGBUILDs
#
# Build source priority:
#   1. Local: Checks /pkgbuilds/<packagename>/ first
#   2. GitHub: If contains "/", fetches from GitHub
#   3. AUR: Otherwise, fetches from AUR
#
# Formats:
#   - Local: packagename [options] (if exists in /pkgbuilds/)
#   - GitHub: owner/repo [options]
#   - AUR: packagename [options]
#
# Options:
#   - skip-pgp: Skip PGP signature verification
#   - install: Install package in container (for dependencies)
#   - always-build: Always build package with timestamp version (unique filename)
#   - source:owner/repo: For -git packages, specify the actual source repo to check for updates
#
# Examples:
#   asdcontrol-git source:nikosdion/asdcontrol  # Uses local PKGBUILD, checks nikosdion/asdcontrol for updates
#   omacom-io/some-package                      # Fetches from GitHub
#   yay                                          # Fetches from AUR

